What We’re Really Looking For
The AI controls the UI — This is not a chatbot. When the user says “send an email to
X”, the compose form visibly fills up. When they say “show last week’s emails”, the inbox
updates. The assistant is a co-pilot that drives the interface.
Clean architecture — Clear separation between mail service, UI, and AI integration.
Easy to follow, easy to extend.
API integration — You can connect to real external services (OAuth, mail APIs, push
notifications).
Pragmatic engineering — Smart trade-offs, clear docs, sensible error handling. Not
over-engineered, not under-built.